title: True Color | Tracey Cunningham
description: My guest today is Tracey Cunningham. Her clients are among the most sought-after women of stage and screen - from JLo to Drew Barrymore, Charlize Theron to Toni Collette, Jennifer Garner to Jessica Biel. She treats her clients like family who have been guided and styled by her for years. And now with the release of her new book, True Color, we all get to be guided by her brilliance.
